casebody.data:
No. 353,

Misc.

Gloria O Towing Corp. v. Byers, U. S. District Judge. Edmund F. Lamb for petitioner. Robert S. Erskine for respondent.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of prohibition and/or mandamus denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit also denied.
